&lt;a href=&#34;https://knowledge4policy.ec.europa.eu/projects-activities/susceptibility-misinformation-during-disasters_en&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
